General.Name: Eisen- und Hüttenwerke AG
General.Description: Eisen- und Hüttenwerke AG engages in the acquisition, management, and sale of investments in businesses that produce and process iron, steel, and other metals and materials in Germany. The company was founded in 1918 and is based in Andernach, Germany. Eisen- und Hüttenwerke AG operates as a subsidiary of ThyssenKrupp Steel Europe AG.
